Ways to create an object.

{ name: 'a' }
new Object()
Object.create({ name: 'a' })
function a(){ return { name: 'a' } }; a()
function a() { this.name = 'a' }; new a()
class a { constructor() { this.name = 'a' } }; new a()

function a() { /* statement */  }
function()   { /* expression */ } 

* functions pass by reference



=======================
1. every object inherits from the Object object
2. functions are objects
3. functions are Function objects
4. Function objects inherit from Object object


